section.div: Random QoL stuff for Spicetify users/devs
Easily make Spicetify extensions and custom apps.

div.div:
Update API entry point to support serverless function integration
This commit modifies the API entry point in `index.ts` to serve as a serverless function that imports the Vike server entry. The change enhances compatibility with Vercel's serverless environment by exporting all necessary components from the server entry, ensuring proper functionality in the deployment setup.

Remove unused serverless function configuration from Vercel setup
This commit simplifies the Vercel configuration by removing the previously defined serverless function for the API entry point. This change reflects the project's current structure and focuses on optimizing the routing setup without unnecessary configurations.

Refactor Tailwind and PostCSS configuration for improved styling management
This commit introduces a new PostCSS configuration file and a TypeScript-based Tailwind configuration, replacing the previous JavaScript configuration. The Vercel configuration is also updated to route API requests to the new TypeScript entry point. This enhances the project's styling capabilities and aligns with modern TypeScript practices.
